[I] The CSV processing CLI

[T] xan is a command line tool that can be used to process CSV files directly
[T] from the shell. It can easily preview, filter, slice, aggregate, sort, join
[T] CSV files, and exposes a large collection of composable commands that can
[T] be chained together to perform a wide variety of typical tasks.

[U] https://github.com/medialab/xan

